Description:
    Stubs out a model and a view for a new cluster 
    task. Pass the task name as the first argument.

Usage:
     script/generate cluster_task TaskName [--advanced]

Options:
     --advanced : will include templates for the advanced
                  PortalTask API methods in the
                  Ruby code template for the task.

Example:

     script/generate cluster_task UniversalTranslator

will create these directories, files and templates:

     app/models/cbrain_task/universal_translator.rb    # symbolic link to cbrain_task_class_loader.rb
     app/models/cbrain_task/universal_translator/
     app/models/cbrain_task/universal_translator/portal/
     app/models/cbrain_task/universal_translator/portal/universal_translator.rb
     app/models/cbrain_task/universal_translator/bourreau/
     app/models/cbrain_task/universal_translator/bourreau/universal_translator.rb
     app/views/tasks/cbrain_task/_universal_translator.html.erb
     app/views/tasks/show_params/_universal_translator.html.erb
     public/doc/tasks/universal_translator_options.html

